@ilyaml218 想和你确认两个问题
1.注册中心是否为redis.
2.是否存在多服务共享dubbo cache目录 （例如挂载盘）。

@L316476844 如果你指的是 spring boot 的话，在入口处设置就好了
```
@SpringBootApplication
public class ProviderApplication {

    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        SpringApplication application = new SpringApplication(ProviderApplication.class);
        application.setRegisterShutdownHook(false);
        application.run(args);
    }
}
```

1 dubbo.service.shutdown.wait需要写在配置文件中dubbo.properties

2 配置了dubbo.service.shutdown.wait的意义是首先停止接收任务，并等待现有任务执行完成，最多等待 XX时间。如果当时没有正在执行的任务，也会立刻停机。

以下是gracefulShutdown代码：

```
public static void gracefulShutdown(Executor executor, int timeout) {
        if (!(executor instanceof ExecutorService) || isShutdown(executor)) {
            return;
        }
        final ExecutorService es = (ExecutorService) executor;
        try {
            es.shutdown(); // Disable new tasks from being submitted
        } catch (SecurityException ex2) {
            return ;
        } catch (NullPointerException ex2) {
            return ;
        }
        try {
            if(! es.awaitTermination(timeout, TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS)) {
                es.shutdownNow();
            }
        } catch (InterruptedException ex) {
            es.shutdownNow();
            Thread.currentThread().interrupt();
        }
        if (!isShutdown(es)){
            newThreadToCloseExecutor(es);
        }
    }
```

